Description: __PreMOn__ (Predicate Model for Ontologies) is a linguistic Linked Data resource representing predicate models such as _PropBank_- _NomBank_- _VerbNet_ and _FrameNet_. PreMOn consists of an OWL ontology for modelling semantic classes with their roles- mappings across different predicate models- and annotations- based on __lemon__ (Lexicon Model for Ontologies); and of a set of RDF datasets for the main predicate models described using this ontology.
